---
title: Sheet Pan Tofu Tikka with Buttery Flatbreads
description: Harness the power of your oven to emulate a tandoor tonight! Spiced tofu and veggies are roasted together to make cleanup a breeze, then covered in an aromatic tikka sauce. A cool cilantro yogurt on top complements all those delicious flavours.

